  - Sacrifice-Death=Death=The Happy Death
By: Eckhart
---
If once a man in intellectual vision did really glimpse the bliss and joy
therein, then all his sufferings, all God intends that he should suffer, would
be a trifle, a mere nothing to him; nay, I say more, it would be pure joy and
pleasure.
